These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, fanta, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, camping, reading, drawing
4 different pets are kept: horse, turtle, guinea-pig, goat
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, ebony, white, apricot
1. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
6. the person who likes white is the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | mirinda   | coffee  | fanta  |
| Hobby   | camping    | drawing    | fishing      | reading    |
| Pet   | goat | turtle | guinea-pig | horse |
| Color     | apricot  | chestnut       | ebony    | white     |

