.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, march, april
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, reggae, funk, hip-hop
4 different games are played: billiard, whist, canasta, bridge
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, zinnia, bellflower, iris
1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
3. the person playing bridge is the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the fan hip-hop is between the person playing canasta and the person who growsorchid##2
6. the person who growsiris is between the fan hip-hop and the person playing bridge##2
7. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
8. the fan reggae is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
9. the fan funk is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | april | february    | march  | may    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | reggae  | hip-hop  | funk |
| Game           | bridge      | canasta       | whist      | billiard       |
| Flower         | zinnia    | iris | bellflower | orchid |

