.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
City: new-york, hannover, berlin, prague
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, blood-red, chestnut, red
4 different games are played: whist, snooker, scrabble, mah-jongg
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, funk, gospel, ambient
1. the person playing scrabble is the fan funk##1
2. the fan funk is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the fan gospel is on the left of the fan funk##1
4. the fan funk is on the left of the fan jazz##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
6. the person playing snooker is the person who likes red##1
7. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes red##2
9. the person who likes chestnut is between the person traveling to berlin and the person playing snooker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| City        | hannover | berlin     | new-york   | prague     |
| Color       | blood-red   | turquise   | chestnut | red |
| Game         | whist   | scrabble | mah-jongg       | snooker    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | funk | jazz  | ambient    |

