 5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is the townhouse house##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the victorian house is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
10. the ranch-style house is between the person drinking juice and the palace house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| House           | victorian  | palace | ranch-style     | townhouse |
| Birthday   | september | august  | january | february       |
| Beverage           | sprite       | almond-milk    | coffee      | juice           |
| Cigar         | old-henry | aristoff   | dunhill   | vegafina         |

