.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, turtle, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, helicopter, taxi, trike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, ice-hockey, swimming, cycling
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, siglo, tiparillo, baccarat
 1. the owner of the cat is between the baccarat-smoker and the owner of the turtle##2
 2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the roller##2
 4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the cat is the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
